7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both ChatGPT and TextCortex share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Short Form, Tone Control, Multilingual. On the other hand, TextCortex uniquely offers Templates and Browser Extension, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, ChatGPT holds an overall score of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 10/10, while TextCortex scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both ChatGPT and TextCortex offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. ChatGPT's free tier and TextCortex's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
